title: Diary
author: kaelthas88
pages:
#- It's al right, mother. It's almost over. So very close. How long have we struggled? How long have we waited? Too long, I know. But it's almost over. I promise.

killhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhimkillhim
